I"Ï<p>Do you know what happens when you throw unicorn poop into a fan?
It makes everything better, everyone and everything around looks perfect, covered with joy and happiness.
Working seriously on (public or private) APIs can lead to the same kind of effect on how we build software.
Why?
Because modern web APIs raises the bar of software design and developer experience and so raises awareness and expectations regarding these topics for software in general.</p>
